    "passages": [
      {
        "id": "Introduction",
        "text": "<p>You are a SOC Analyst at The Overdraft Emporium. A mid-size regional financial institution known for its friendly service but relaxed approach to internal cybersecurity protocols.</p><p>The company values efficiency and dislikes “unnecessary interruptions.”</p>",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Continue",
            "next": "Continue"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "Continue",
        "text": "<p>At 9:36 AM, you receive an alert that a mass phishing campaign is targeting employees. The emails appear to come from the CFO, urging users to “change their passwords immediately” using a link provided.</p>",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Run AV scans on all network devices",
            "next": "Run-AV-scans-on-all-network-devices",
            "penalty": 10,
            "mistake": "Running an AV scan is an investigation action, but quarantining the active threat is a higher priority containment step."
          },
          {
            "text": "Quarantine the emails for investigation",
            "next": "Quarantine-the-emails-for-investigation",
            "penalty": 0
          },
          {
            "text": "Personally investigate the link (Sandbox)",
            "next": "Personally-investigate-the-link-Sand-box",
            "penalty": 5,
            "mistake": "Prioritized analysis over the containment of the active email threat."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "Run-AV-scans-on-all-network-devices",
