        "text": "<p>You decide to close the incident and flag it as a false positive. Later that day, however, multiple employees report being locked out after “resetting” their passwords using the phishing link.</p><p>You now realize that the link was a positive alert which you have now reported to the CISO.</p>",
        "choices": [
