        "text": "<p>You closed the incident, and all is well.</p><p>A month later a similar occurence surges as you had failed to porperly check for any employees who had exposed their accounts by access the phishing link</p><p>You are able to recover and prevent it once again, but at the loss of time and money for the company.</p><div class=\"ascii-art\"><br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⡀⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠈⠄⠄⠄⠁⠄⠁⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⣀⣀⣤⣤⣴⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣦⣤⣤⣄⣀⡀⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⣴⣿⣿⡿⣿⢿⣟⣿⣻⣟⡿⣟⣿⣟⡿⣟⣿⣻⣟⣿⣻⢿⣻⡿⣿⢿⣷⣆⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⢘⣿⢯⣷⡿⡿⡿⢿⢿⣷⣯⡿⣽⣞⣷⣻⢯⣷⣻⣾⡿⡿⢿⢿⢿⢯⣟⣞⡮⡀⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⢸⢞⠟⠃⣉⢉⠉⠉⠓⠫⢿⣿⣷⢷⣻⣞⣿⣾⡟⠽⠚⠊⠉⠉⠉⠙⠻⣞⢵⠂⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⢜⢯⣺⢿⣻⣿⣿⣷⣔⡄⠄⠈⠛⣿⣿⡾⠋⠁⠄⠄⣄⣶⣾⣿⡿⣿⡳⡌⡗⡅⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⢽⢱⢳⢹⡪⡞⠮⠯⢯⡻⡬⡐⢨⢿⣿⣿⢀⠐⡥⣻⡻⠯⡳⢳⢹⢜⢜⢜⢎⠆⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠠⣻⢌⠘⠌⡂⠈⠁⠉⠁⠘⠑⢧⣕⣿⣿⣿⢤⡪⠚⠂⠈⠁⠁⠁⠂⡑⠡⡈⢮⠅⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠠⣳⣿⣿⣽⣭⣶⣶⣶⣶⣶⣺⣟⣾⣻⣿⣯⢯⢿⣳⣶⣶⣶⣖⣶⣮⣭⣷⣽⣗⠍⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⢀⢻⡿⡿⣟⣿⣻⣽⣟⣿⢯⣟⣞⡷⣿⣿⣯⢿⢽⢯⣿⣻⣟⣿⣻⣟⣿⣻⢿⣿⢀⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⡑⡏⠯⡯⡳⡯⣗⢯⢟⡽⣗⣯⣟⣿⣿⣾⣫⢿⣽⠾⡽⣺⢳⡫⡞⡗⡝⢕⠕⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⢂⡎⠅⡃⢇⠇⠇⣃⣧⡺⡻⡳⡫⣿⡿⣟⠞⠽⠯⢧⣅⣃⠣⠱⡑⡑⠨⢐⢌⠂⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠐⠼⣦⢀⠄⣶⣿⢿⣿⣧⣄⡌⠂⠢⠩⠂⠑⣁⣅⣾⢿⣟⣷⠦⠄⠄⡤⡇⡪⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠨⢻⣧⡅⡈⠛⠿⠿⠿⠛⠁⠄⢀⡀⠄⠄⠘⠻⠿⠿⠯⠓⠁⢠⣱⡿⢑⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠈⢌⢿⣷⡐⠤⣀⣀⣂⣀⢀⢀⡓⠝⡂⡀⢀⢀⢀⣀⣀⠤⢊⣼⡟⡡⡁⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠈⢢⠚⣿⣄⠈⠉⠛⠛⠟⠿⠿⠟⠿⠻⠻⠛⠛⠉⠄⣠⠾⢑⠰⠈⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠑⢌⠿⣦⡡⣱⣸⣸⣆⠄⠄⠄⣰⣕⢔⢔⠡⣼⠞⡡⠁⠁⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠑⢝⢷⣕⡷⣿⡿⠄⠄⠠⣿⣯⣯⡳⡽⡋⠌⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠙⢮⣿⣽⣯⠄⠄⢨⣿⣿⡷⡫⠃⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠘⠙⠝⠂⠄⢘⠋⠃⠁⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄<br>⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄</div>",
